Medium: One double-sided folio of an unbound artist’s book with ink, colored ink, ballpoint pen, felt-tip pen, watercolor, and cut-and-pasted colored paper on 34 folded double-sided sheets of paper and a found painted silk sheet with a stamp and label
CreditLine: Latin American and Caribbean Fund and Agnes Gund
